This week, 'freshwater hero,' acclaimed photographer, and creator of the Disney+ documentary 'Into the Canyon' @pedromcbride and @joshjesperson, fellow river conservationist and creator of the upcoming film, the Animas Project join us to discuss conservation, abandoning ego, and how we can help fight back against the greatest threats to our water systems today. 

Visit the link in our profile to listen 🎧⁠⁠

Sponsored by @theadventureactivist.⁠⁠

@nnieguglia is a Professional Skateboarder from Montreal, Canada. Rather than hitting the same spots all year, Annie decided to head to Colorado in her RV taking in the open space, colors, and concrete skateparks. 

We joined Annie for a few days on and off the grid with her friend @alexisfortin83 to hit some of Colorado's best skateparks. Between skating and meeting with friends, Annie and Alexis head off the grid to cook, camp, and enjoy the beauty of the Rocky Mountains.

Presented by @therealgorv! 

More at http://bit.ly/Boundless-Ep-5 

#GORV #ROAM #BOUNDLESS #RV

Presented by @therealgorv!⁠⠀

Annie Guglia is a Professional Skateboarder from Montreal, CA. Rather than hitting the same spots all year, Annie decided to head to Colorado in her RV taking in the open space, colors, and concrete skateparks. ⁠
⁠
We joined Annie for a weekend on and off the grid with her friend Alexis to hit some of Colorado's best skateparks. Between skating and meeting with friends, Annie and Alexis head off the grid to cook, camp, and enjoy the beauty of the Rocky Mountains.⁠
⁠
More at the Link in bio! 

http://bit.ly/Boundless-Ep-5 ⁠
⁠
#GORV #ROAM #BOUNDLESS #RV

Presented by @TheRealGORV! 

Griff Washburn aka @GothBabemusic is a Musician, Surfer, and Climber.  Rather than going to the same recording studio, Griff built one in his RV allowing him to put music secondary and live life to the fullest.

We Joined Griff for a weekend off the grid with his partner Cate and dog, Sadie to explore his songwriting process, love for rock climbing, and source of inspiration. Seeking adventure and a one of a kind view of Mt. Hood, we joined the crew on French's Dome for a day of climbing and music. 

#GORV #ROAM #BOUNDLESS #RV

Rock climbing assignments are some of my favorite. They can be very involved, but are often with my closest friends. node.text:
Starry nights over the great plains of Wyoming. This image hardly has any post processing on it, I vividly remember staring up at the sky mouth wide open in pure awe of what I was witnessing. The stillness was broken only by a few shooting stars here and there. The sounds of the crickets and frogs echoed across the water. It was truly an immersive moment out in the wild. 

Photo and words by Roam contributor @scottcrady 

#Wyoming  #nightsky #stars

Let the spirit of your adventures inspire your creativity in the kitchen (or at the campsite!) and use recipes that help you tune into nature. Lentine teaches you her tactical skills, how she stocks her RV, and how to make her delicious recipes from breakfast to dinner and everything in between. Free downloadable recipes available for all of her recipes.

As Lentine says, “food and the knowledge of what fuels us has the power to unlock our wildest dreams, greatest potential and ultimate joy.”
